title: Batman Beyond v5 1-26 (2012-2013) (Digital) (Ongoing) (Empire)
description:
English | CBR and CBZ | 26 Issues

Batman Beyond v5 #1-26
Publisher:  DC Comics
Publication Date:  February 15, 2012 - July 6, 2013

Writer:  Adam Beechen
Artists:  Norm Breyfogle (#1-18, 21), Adam Archer (#22-26)
Penciller:  Peter Nguyen (#19-20)
Inker:  Craig Yeung (#19-20)
Colorist:  Andrew Elder
Letterer:  Saida Temofonte
Cover Artists:  Dustin Nguyen (#1-18), Ryan Benjamin (#19-20), Norm Breyfogle and Andrew Elder (#21-26)

This Batman Beyond series is a digital first series which is released sometimes monthly and sometimes bimonthly.  This series as well as Justice League Beyond and Superman Beyond are collected in the monthly print series Batman Beyond Unlimited.

New adventures of the future Batman! Terry McGinnis is back in his high tech Bat-suit, patrolling the gleaming spires of Gotham under the watchful eye of Bruce Wayne, the original Dark Knight. But balancing school, personal life and crime fighting duties may be his biggest challenge.

Thanks goes to ZOOM, Zone, Nahga, K6, and Son of Ultron for this release.
